{"tid":480934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一年容易又露營2017秋-地點，裝備","createTime":"2017-11-26T15:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T13:45:03.000Z","uid":11066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"833a931c3e8db13f1d9dbfeff1b23a0c9f8fcf92","tid":480934,"uid":11066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"今日行完東霸，應該差唔多露營時候<br />\n咁多位巴打有冇咩新裝備，地點推薦？<br />\n<br />\n個NH舊營用左兩年左右想換, 睇中隻兩邊雙開既NH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過成6舊人仔好似太貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/234613_414623bb308f249e5ddf7fce3aa5fb37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F234613_414623bb308f249e5ddf7fce3aa5fb37.jpg&h=1236d317&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d161366b11ef6538120e9750c67d92d61f9a58fa","tid":480934,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"982830dc1475008cbf6fbdbac3da6b8c834e975d","tid":480934,"uid":11066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"今年d巴打未出動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b895b010607e43107655baa69dba659e84088d8","tid":480934,"uid":131127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:45:39.000Z","msg":"其實裝備同地點年年都係果堆🤣 灣西灣南貝澳南山呢堆... 細場或者x 位通常都唔會share 因為一講就又變旺角"},{"pid":"1b7a24f2e234fbb708ab388ee84ebe921ee07e9e","tid":480934,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"樓主隻營有咩特別，點解淘寶都咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a53fdb28258d6cfc39c142d23cc529f7b2d513","tid":480934,"uid":30096,"like":0,"d