es/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知有咩特別，唯一兩邊有門通風，好多nh營都係一邊門only<br />\n<br />\nBtw露營野好似連淘寶都貴左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去親露營都見有人用nh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪愈來愈多人用，慢慢咁加左價<br />\n依家望好似都唔平得去邊咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想買個營要6舊水"},{"pid":"4afa6e22294dde341002956276985047e7370456","tid":480934,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"用緊msr, nemo, marmot"},{"pid":"e3156c01634c8334fa8f8c1f8dc087bce8a8461c","tid":480934,"uid":11066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"其實要用行山杖起既營同一般營骨有咩分別？"},{"pid":"c9876a7ca93bb99a8024503e87b250e6f8a83d0c","tid":480934,"uid":131127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊msr, nemo, marmot</blockquote><br />\n前兩隻香港用都要好小心打理🤣<br />\nbtw marmot 既營幾大隻又唔貴👍<br />\n幾正呢"},{"pid":"0fa40b670d55153f2c06898d4e0f766b526ac349","tid":480934,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實要用行山杖起既營同一般營骨有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n玩得輕個營拉風繩有d技巧"},{"pid":"dfe29b9964cd21584fceec386534a4ad14ca5773","tid":480934,"uid":131127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實要用行山杖起既營同一般營骨有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n最大分別係在於用行山杖起既營一定係non-freestand, 用營骨既營就可以係freestand 或者non-freeatand.<br />\n<br />\nfreestand 姐係唔洗落任何釘, 扣好晒營骨, 落晒外帳就可以用 呢個係呢類營既特點亦係優點. 方便係d 地好細或者無得落釘既地方用. 缺點係通常較重.<br />\n<br />\nnon-freestand 就係一定要落釘先起到, 如金仔或者tunnel, 優點係通常較輕(單層營最起見過375g, 雙層係57x g), 缺點係一定要落釘. 如果你個場無位俾你落釘就成隻都起唔到"},{"pid":"0b9dcfb63cd9b2a8618ba0f8b475a939f7c6b5f8","tid":480934,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"近涌好露？<br />\n或者有無推介<br />\n新手"},{"pid":"b380ce1490f5a64a470633de40de6bb7c6233d4c","tid":480934,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>涌背好露？<br />\n或者有無推介<br />\n新手</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb6c0e722f6a1852b4705886afc5124ee034a81a","tid":480934,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>涌背好露？<br />\n或者有無推介<br />\n新手</blockquote></blockquote><br />\ngoogle 下 新新黎黎去去個幾個"},{"pid":"c0d96c12fc4e520aff8559a8b6d33fba0abe2c44","tid":480934,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>涌背好露？<br />\n或者有無推介<br />\n新手</blockquote></blockquote><br />\ngoogle 下 新新黎黎去去個幾個</blockquote><br />\n星期六下午入去會唔會無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb51f2e31b22516864024be6fa1709c799db5c7d","tid":480934,"uid":50408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"返緊運動用品鋪<br />\n每賣一個營就會諗又多一個人爭位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6597a3a73265eb49a967120755a3046c9104958","tid":480934,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返緊運動用品鋪<br />\n每賣一個營就會諗又多一個人爭位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人淘寶啦   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37869824c1c7e613ff5dfbbe157c72289bf0805","tid":480934,"uid":11066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實要用行山杖起既營同一般營骨有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n最大分別係在於用行山杖起既營一定係non-freestand, 用營骨既營就可以係freestand 或者non-freeatand.<br /